metadata.name: CyberSyndicate #0001
metadata.description: Cyber Syndicate is a Voxel art metaverse project leveraging The Sandbox's land and game mechanics. Based in Cyber City, this innovative and futuristic project incorporates NFTs with rich Cyberpunk inspired lore, forming the base for numerous Web3 activities and experiences. The release of 3,333 unique 3D VX gaming avatars will unlock a variety of access perks and rewards for avatar owners.
